<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 02:28:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>调查显示定居者对巴勒斯坦村庄的突袭是在以色列国防军面前进行的，而以色列国防军却没有采取任何行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/investigation-shows-settler-raid-on-palestinian-village-took-place-in-front-of-idf-forces/00000191-5ce6-d7bf-a5b9-fcf66a940000</link><description>一名高级国防官员说，士兵们“没有采取任何行动来阻止大屠杀，他们只是站在旁边，看着这一切[发生]，但什么也没做。”被杀巴勒斯坦人的尸体已被带去尸检，但结果无法确定是谁射杀了他</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 22:18:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/investigation-shows-settler-raid-on-palestinian-village-took-place-in-front-of-idf-forces/00000191-5ce6-d7bf-a5b9-fcf66a940000</guid></item><item><title>尽管发生了战争，议会平民准备委员会已经几个月没有召开会议了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/despite-war-knesset-committee-on-civilian-preparedness-hasnt-convened-for-months/00000191-5b80-d101-a7fd-7bbf13a30000</link><description>消息人士称，由于委员会讨论的议题较多，除了小组委员会的密切监督和深入讨论外，别无选择，距离小组委员会上次召开会议已经过去了四个月，这危及了以色列的国家安全</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 18:33:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/despite-war-knesset-committee-on-civilian-preparedness-hasnt-convened-for-months/00000191-5b80-d101-a7fd-7bbf13a30000</guid></item><item><title>“像我这样的犹太人不再在左派中感到受欢迎”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jews-like-me-no-longer-feel-welcome-on-the-left/00000191-50e4-d50b-adff-72e792a50000</link><description>对于澳大利亚最著名的记者之一、前自称为“反犹太复国主义联邦主义者”的迈克尔·加文达来说，10 月 7 日是一个警钟。随着他的祖国反犹太主义的高涨，特别是在他曾经视为盟友的群体中，他担心澳大利亚的犹太人</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 17:17:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jews-like-me-no-longer-feel-welcome-on-the-left/00000191-50e4-d50b-adff-72e792a50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列自以为强大，但从未如此依赖美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-thinks-its-strong-but-has-never-been-so-dependent-on-the-u-s/00000191-5b22-d392-a995-7fe6d4e10000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来，美国已三度向中东派遣主力部队，帮助以色列对抗伊朗及其代理人 — — 除了大规模军事援助外。这是关系的悖论：在内塔尼亚胡的领导下，以色列感觉越强大，就越依赖美国</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 17:08:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-thinks-its-strong-but-has-never-been-so-dependent-on-the-u-s/00000191-5b22-d392-a995-7fe6d4e10000</guid></item><item><title>调解人称，美国提出停火建议，在以色列和哈马斯之间架起桥梁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-presents-cease-fire-proposal-that-bridges-israel-hamas-mediators-say/00000191-5bb4-d101-a7fd-7bbfda890000</link><description>据调解员称，该提案“有助于迅速实施协议” ■ 预计谈判将于下周在开罗继续进行</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 16:34:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-presents-cease-fire-proposal-that-bridges-israel-hamas-mediators-say/00000191-5bb4-d101-a7fd-7bbfda890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 315 天：拜登称谈判各方“比以往任何时候都更接近”停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-315-biden-says-negotiating-parties-closer-than-ever-to-cease-fire/00000191-5bff-dc4c-a59f-7bff300f0001</link><description>停火/人质释放协议的谈判周五在卡塔尔继续进行，一位消息人士称，他们“到目前为止已经取得了成功” ■ 接近真主党的消息人士告诉《华盛顿邮报》，只要谈判正在进行，真主党就不会报复以色列多哈 ■ 以色列外长告诉英国和法国外长，“如果伊朗发动袭击，我们预计联军不仅会与以色列一起防御” ■ 战争已过去 315 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 16:26:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-315-biden-says-negotiating-parties-closer-than-ever-to-cease-fire/00000191-5bff-dc4c-a59f-7bff300f0001</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯人质的父亲说：“如果内塔尼亚胡想要达成协议，这次采访就不会进行”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/if-netanyahu-wanted-a-deal-this-interview-wouldnt-have-taken-place/00000191-5b72-d101-a7fd-7bffd9ed0000</link><description>伊齐克·霍恩（Itzik Horn）花了数周时间并承受了巨大的压力才得知他的两个儿子亚伊尔（Yair）和埃坦（Eitan）被关押在加沙。这位阿根廷出生的父亲猛烈抨击那些“背着人质”为加沙带来秩序的人，并建议内塔尼亚胡派他的儿子亚伊尔前往加沙，带回霍恩的儿子亚伊尔</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 14:59:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/if-netanyahu-wanted-a-deal-this-interview-wouldnt-have-taken-place/00000191-5b72-d101-a7fd-7bffd9ed0000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日已经足够令人震惊了。以色列人为何要粉饰这场悲剧？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/october-7-was-shocking-enough-why-should-israelis-embellish-the-tragedy/00000191-5a8b-d316-a9f1-decb1be60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 14:27:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/october-7-was-shocking-enough-why-should-israelis-embellish-the-tragedy/00000191-5a8b-d316-a9f1-decb1be60000</guid></item><item><title>美国殖民地酒店希望成为一座理智的岛屿。随后加沙战争爆发</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-american-colony-hotel-hoped-to-be-an-island-of-sanity-then-the-war-broke-out/00000191-5b57-d761-afd9-7f576bf10000</link><description>该酒店是耶路撒冷的地标，但由于入住率直线下降，其生存在其 100 年历史中首次面临危险</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 13:46:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-american-colony-hotel-hoped-to-be-an-island-of-sanity-then-the-war-broke-out/00000191-5b57-d761-afd9-7f576bf10000</guid></item><item><title>总理办公室数据显示，截至 10 月 7 日，内塔尼亚胡已出国六次，花费超过 600 万美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/until-oct-7-netanyahu-flew-abroad-six-times-at-cost-of-over-6-million-pmo-data-shows/00000191-5afa-d101-a7fd-7aff08c70000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在巴黎、罗马和柏林的停留各持续三天，其中巴黎的费用最高，花费了纳税人100万美元。罗马的旅行费用约为 50 万美元，柏林为 302,000 美元</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 12:52:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/until-oct-7-netanyahu-flew-abroad-six-times-at-cost-of-over-6-million-pmo-data-shows/00000191-5afa-d101-a7fd-7aff08c70000</guid></item><item><title>世界必须做出决定：执行加沙授权还是让中东的流血事件继续下去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/the-world-must-decide-implement-gaza-mandate-or-let-the-bloodshed-in-the-region-continue/00000191-5a0a-d753-a395-dbeba59f0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦权力机构没有能力治理加沙，以色列唯一有战后计划的是那些支持吞并的人。虽然让加沙重返托管时代听起来像是另一次殖民主义干预的开始，但事实上，国际机构已经在管理加沙地带</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 09:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/the-world-must-decide-implement-gaza-mandate-or-let-the-bloodshed-in-the-region-continue/00000191-5a0a-d753-a395-dbeba59f0000</guid></item><item><title>犹太定居者袭击西岸村庄；巴勒斯坦人死亡，一人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-vows-to-prosecute-israeli-settlers-after-deadly-riots-in-west-bank-village/00000191-57a6-dacb-a7bf-f7ae83f10000</link><description>周四晚上，数十名犹太定居者突然袭击吉特，造成至少一人死亡；亚伊尔·戈兰：“定居者是一个暴力团体，得到政府的大力支持”</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 07:53:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-vows-to-prosecute-israeli-settlers-after-deadly-riots-in-west-bank-village/00000191-57a6-dacb-a7bf-f7ae83f10000</guid></item><item><title>加沙停火、人质谈判将于周五继续；卡塔尔总理向伊朗通报了谈判进展情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/gaza-cease-fire-hostage-talks-to-continue-friday-qatari-pm-updated-iran-on-progress/00000191-59a8-db91-a7dd-7fa8abb50000</link><description>一位消息人士告诉《国土报》，“双方希望在未来 24 小时内看到进展”。伊朗还收到了谈判的最新情况，表明伊朗间接参与了谈判，以及美国、卡塔尔和埃及为防止伊朗和真主党升级而做出的努力</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 06:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/gaza-cease-fire-hostage-talks-to-continue-friday-qatari-pm-updated-iran-on-progress/00000191-59a8-db91-a7dd-7fa8abb50000</guid></item><item><title>“现在，在以色列，人们已经撤离家园。但我们从一个星球搬到了另一个星球”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/now-many-israelis-have-evacuated-their-homes-but-we-moved-from-one-planet-to-another/00000191-5929-d316-a9f1-dde9fd4c0000</link><description>她经历过失落、拒绝和局外人的痛苦，但从未离开过舞台。 94 岁高龄的以色列剧院第一夫人 Lea Koenig 谈论如何才能过上长久而有意义的生活</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 04:19:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/now-many-israelis-have-evacuated-their-homes-but-we-moved-from-one-planet-to-another/00000191-5929-d316-a9f1-dde9fd4c0000</guid></item><item><title>“当我从我的与生俱来的权利之旅回到家时，我将开始去犹太教堂”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-16/ty-article/.highlight/when-i-get-back-home-from-my-birthright-trip-ill-start-going-to-synagogue/00000191-592a-d316-a9f1-ddeab4d10000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一位从小信奉天主教长大的美国人在以色列之行中学到了很多东西，而一位以色列人则因为“神灵把他送到那里”而进入萨满教</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 03:40:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-08-16/ty-article/.highlight/when-i-get-back-home-from-my-birthright-trip-ill-start-going-to-synagogue/00000191-592a-d316-a9f1-ddeab4d10000</guid></item><item><title>美国人正在发放胡萝卜，但内塔尼亚胡更担心国内的大棒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/the-americans-are-handing-out-carrots-but-netanyahus-more-worried-about-sticks-at-home/00000191-56da-dc4c-a59f-7eff397e0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的所有考虑因素在多哈发生冲突 ■ 美国人对以色列对哈马斯的破坏程度感到惊讶，但相信它已经取得了所能做到的一切 ■ 真主党与以色列建立了恐惧平衡，但也处于劣势</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 03:06:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/the-americans-are-handing-out-carrots-but-netanyahus-more-worried-about-sticks-at-home/00000191-56da-dc4c-a59f-7eff397e0000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩是一个民族的两个国家——两个国家都在等待真主党</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-is-two-states-for-one-people-and-both-of-them-are-waiting-for-hezbollah/00000191-57e5-db91-a7dd-77edf0330000</link><description>多哈停火谈判的进展将决定黎巴嫩停止敌对行动的时间表，但目前尚不清楚真主党在峰会后将如何表现 — — 以及是否同意放弃对刺杀高级指挥官的报复袭击</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 03:00:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-is-two-states-for-one-people-and-both-of-them-are-waiting-for-hezbollah/00000191-57e5-db91-a7dd-77edf0330000</guid></item><item><title>我们在以色列的斯德泰曼基地服役。这是我们对被拘留在那里的加沙人所做的事情</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/we-served-on-israels-sde-teiman-base-heres-what-we-did-to-gazans-detainees/00000191-5591-d60d-a59b-ff994cb40000</link><description>手脚都戴着镣铐。眼睛被蒙住了。不动。不说话。有时还会遭到暴力殴打。日复一日，周复一周，在斯德泰曼关押哈马斯恐怖分子和加沙巴勒斯坦平民的设施中就这样过去了。这些受访者都知道。他们在那里服役</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 03:00:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/we-served-on-israels-sde-teiman-base-heres-what-we-did-to-gazans-detainees/00000191-5591-d60d-a59b-ff994cb40000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩报道：以色列对黎巴嫩南部发动空袭，造成 6 人死亡、3 人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article-live/.premium/netanyahu-israeli-leaders-condemn-deadly-settler-violence-idf-shin-bet-to-investigate/00000191-5905-d316-a9f1-ddc52c520000</link><description>报道：真主党不会在卡塔尔谈判期间对以色列发动袭击，报复“并不紧急” ■ 蒙面定居者袭击约旦河西岸村庄后，巴勒斯坦人被杀；美国谴责袭击事件 ■ 停火、释放人质谈判在卡塔尔继续进行 ■ 法国、英国外长将在耶路撒冷会见以色列外长</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 02:42:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article-live/.premium/netanyahu-israeli-leaders-condemn-deadly-settler-violence-idf-shin-bet-to-investigate/00000191-5905-d316-a9f1-ddc52c520000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普、哈里斯在民主党大会前竞选活动中犹太人投票为零</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/trump-harris-campaigns-zero-in-on-jewish-vote-ahead-of-democratic-convention/00000191-58ce-db91-a7dd-7fce1ee40000</link><description>在这次选举中，以色列和反犹太主义可能比以往任何一场选举都更受关注，两个阵营都利用明星影响力、巨额捐助者和网络来争取犹太社区的支持</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 02:14:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/trump-harris-campaigns-zero-in-on-jewish-vote-ahead-of-democratic-convention/00000191-58ce-db91-a7dd-7fce1ee40000</guid></item></channel></rss>